{"tid":1794559,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"救手足！ - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-23T08:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T08:29:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7100a4b30c9b26ec9c1b761a3ec182a6d3f05e","tid":1794559,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191223/20829910/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829910%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwePMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=6988d19e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829910%2F&h=c7f895ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191223/20829910/</a><br />\n<br />\n救手足！ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191223/large/1577000264_2d1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577000264_2d1a.jpg&h=c3b742b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這幾天的政治風雲人物，不是獻媚不遺餘力的奴才，而是「什麼也不做」的白襪仔波叔。<br />\n<br />\n作為林鄭夫君，不得不陪同出席澳門慶回歸盛會，習大大訪澳，一眾諂笑相迎（香港代表是彎腰半鞠躬握手的紅裙千嬅嬸嬸），無數嘉賓十足機械人，一邊唱《歌唱祖國》，一邊大打拍子，集體表態，無一倖免？不，從《人民日報》發放影片所見，與林鄭、外交部部長、港澳辦主任等奴才並列的林兆波，雙手交加放前，並無興奮表情，不打拍子不唱紅歌不動如山，相當突出，即使拍攝的鏡頭「尷尬」，他亦出污泥而不染，堅持自我。連登仔以及各界人士，都認為波叔身處龍潭虎穴，是真正勇武的前線手足，敬佩不已。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭不但搞唔掂示威者，連同床異夢貌合神離的老公和兒子也沒轍。不過陰毒得以兩三代年輕人的血來餵飼黑警的妹仔，也不在乎人倫了。<br />\n<br />\n──所以，前線悽厲的吶喊「救手足！」，得關注波叔，他所犯的是死罪，不知那英國公民護照能罩多久？秋後算帳，可能被捕、關押精神病院、困集中營，或成為被上吊被跳樓被跳海（全裸無可疑）的屍體&hellip;&hellip;林手足家門不幸，娶了個令祖宗蒙羞的香港歷史罪人，還隨時因略振夫綱而送命，大家要從禮崩府或人質屋把他救出來，護送回英呀！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1c42f7529e3841ab68edc0b1a85bef2867a520e9","tid":1794559,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">稅局聖誕激光燈飾之夜</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n19:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「星火不息 燃點國際」集會</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n時間︰晚上七時至九時<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦方︰張崑陽、候任中西區區議員梁晃維、民間集會團隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲警方發出不反對通知書</span>"},{"pid":"71f664082cf21dd2eb3e727e3618c8f341b63ceb","tid":1794559,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林家不幸"},{"pid":"abb74200024e63ffbacf7db537ed8237bbd6712d","tid":1794559,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3db99acbb96bae3cd71ef526ea06f97541566de","tid":1794559,"uid":329551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"雙規驊喺英國都被綁返首都，然後「被煲粥」。英國廢物，都保佢唔住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林生作爲呢場抗爭有歷史以來最前線手足，RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}